


   #  Schema discovery Based on Partition is possible now(For Paruqet)
   #  Data types,
      +  Are inferred by default
         -  can be disabled by setting 'spark.sql.sources.partitionColumnTypeInference.enabled=false'
            .  All columns will be considered as 'string'
            
            
